Apache::Voodoo
==============

Apache Voodoo, or just Voodoo for short is a web based application framework
for Apache 1.3, Apache 2 and mod_perl. 

See http://www.apachevoodoo.com for more details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

